{"tid":1653544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認識美國國旗","createTime":"2019-10-14T06:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T12:54:18.000Z","uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7926c19755bfd60f31a0f1724b838c242301760f","tid":1653544,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/52SHBTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52SHBTg.jpg&h=555fd876&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAccY6B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAccY6B.jpg&h=0c7b75fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國旗旗面由13道紅白相間的寬條構成，左上角還有一個包含了50顆白色小五角星的藍色長方形。50顆小星代表了美國的50個州，而13條間紋則象徵著美國最早建國時的13個殖民地。紅色象徵勇氣，白色象徵真理，藍色則象徵正義。 這面旗幟俗稱「星條旗」、中文俗稱「花旗」，正式名稱「合眾國旗」。"},{"pid":"a3c94f682835668f6f4268f768126b1ed470981c","tid":1653544,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:47:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77312482bb3bc45061958102007c19f1a8e8524e","tid":1653544,"uid":251083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T12:54:18.000Z","msg":"感謝介紹"}]}